parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can result in serious injury or death in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or deploy late, leaving occupants vulnerable to impact.
symptoms: Airbag light illuminates on the dashboard
airbag failure to deploy in a crash
delayed airbag deployment
failure of both driver and passenger side airbags to deploy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag light on the dashboard indicates a malfunction within the system, which can lead to airbag failure in the event of a crash, putting occupants at risk.
symptoms: Airbag light illuminates on the dashboard
unknown cause of malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelts to lock up during a crash can result in serious injury or death, as occupants may not be properly restrained.
symptoms: Seatbelts do not lock up during a crash
failure of seatbelts to restrain occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate, jerk, or stall while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch or pressure plate can cause the vehicle to hesitate, jerk, or stall while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle hesitates or jerks when shifting gears
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.
